Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:02.14,Roger Monologue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:03.94,Roger Monologue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gold Roger, the king of the pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.94,Roger Monologue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}obtained everything \Nthe world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:09.90,Roger Monologue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His final words lured all sorts\Nof adventurers to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:13.36,Roger Monologue,,0,0,0,,My treasure? \NIt's yours, if you can find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:17.45,Roger Monologue,,0,0,0,,Everything is right where I left it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:24.29,Roger Monologue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now pirates head for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:25.63,Roger Monologue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The world has entered...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.63,Roger Monologue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Great Pirate Era!
